					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2238524#post-2830267</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2238524/spc-2000#post-2830267</link>
				<description></description>
